CatDescriptText: March of Dimes posters with handicapped children are included in display case with additional advertisements that read "The Ravens, They Are Appearing Hear for the Interest of the...March of Dimes  Immediately After Their Performance at the Roosevelt Theatre Music By LeRoy Brown for Dancing, MC Cornell Cooper, Guest Band George Hudson and His Band".
